Maybe you're psychic.

100
00:04:55,061 --> 00:04:58,725
Just use my phone
to call the kids.

101
00:04:58,799 --> 00:05:00,233
Why do you need yours?

102
00:05:00,333 --> 00:05:02,734
You know that they won't pick
up now and then when you leave,

103
00:05:02,903 --> 00:05:05,065
