when they get back.

224
00:10:09,976 --> 00:10:11,308
Okay.

225
00:10:11,744 --> 00:10:12,871
Whoa!

226
00:10:12,946 --> 00:10:14,746
Hang on, I thought that
you were staying here.

227
00:10:15,215 --> 00:10:17,878
Older woman,
unresponsive, needs a doctor.

228
