She's in cardiogenic shock.

236
00:10:45,945 --> 00:10:47,277
I will page Dr. Reynolds.

237
00:10:47,347 --> 00:10:49,646
There's nothing you can do.

238
00:10:49,749 --> 00:10:52,275
